<a name="staff_of_the_observers"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Staff of the Observers</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/staff_of_the_observers.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">2H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 7.14<BR>
Damage 12 - Delay 35<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - BAR, DEF, ERU, GNM, HEF, HIE, HUM, ELF<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/shaman/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/wizard/weapons/2h_blunt.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/sentinel.shtml?spellID=333">Sentinel</a><BR>
Charges: 50<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +5) (WIS +5) (Mana +30) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/staff_of_the_observers.shtml?questID=88">Staff of the Observers</a> quest<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 404pp (80 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 338pp (4 quotes)<BR>

