<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>In order to use the sentinel spell on the staff you must click or double-click (unsure)on it in your inventory.  An easy way to do this is to make the malee slot (where the staff is) as one of the hotkeys.  Pressing the hotkeys should make the staff go off.<BR>
<BR>
I know that I have to do this process to use the spell on my summoned staff of warding.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck.</font></td></tr></table>
