<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Fumor</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-20 00:05:14</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have had my Staff of the Observers from lvl 17 to lvl 28 and I still have. If you get the staff my advice is NEVER use sentinel if you are anywhere near another player. It will annoy the heck out of them. One time one of my friends did in High Keep everybody in the zone went crazy and chased him out. So if you don't want this to happen to you don't use sentinel, btw it doesn't really have a use. For the person who said it was good for camping, it isn't. The sentinel follows you around. But the damage is pretty good and the wis, int and mana are well worth it.<BR>
<BR>
My 2cp</font></td></tr></table>
