<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hey, thought I would let you know something that might help getting the staff with bad faction.  My Druid con'd Apprehensive to Brona Frugrin, so what I did was log, create a gnome, bring gnome to Brona (good faction) log, come back with Druid drop the lens log, come back with gnome pick up lens give to Brona, she gives me the Staff, drop the staff log, come back on with Druid pick up staff and gate.</font></td></tr></table>
