<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Awesome staff.  I'm a lvl 17 Wiz and got it easy because I was luckily in the right place in the right time - A high level necro had just came back from runnyeye and sold the Evil eye to me for 50pp. I quickly ran back to Steamfront, no problems with faction since I'm a gnome.  The damage is very nice since I'm hitting for maximum 22dmg; I actually outdamage most of the fighters in my group (102dmg spells and 22dmg malee) .  The light given off by the staff is actually better than a gls.  I highly recomend this staff to all the casters out there.  It really made my life a lot easier</font></td></tr></table>
